[media]
# Play the Free Demo Now!
You are a prisoner with a life sentence and one last chance. They are sending you into the Cube, a digital prison of perfect squares, after reports of dangerous irregularities. 

[media]
# Find Out What's Inside the Cube
No one will say what is inside; only that someone like you is expendable enough to find out.

[media]
# No Turning Back
When the door closes behind you, there's no turning back. Only the dark cuboid corridor lies ahead. What will you find?

[media]
# Thank You
... for your voluntary participation.
